{"title":"蒋区公务员  呈请涨价","authors":["马凡陀"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":6,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋区公务员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈请涨价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马凡陀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窃查职等薪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本属微薄可怜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迩来物价波动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人价益见低廉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上次公用事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮电交通煤炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以致上涨数倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"业经实行在案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当时钧座表示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"职等公教人员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亦将调整薪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千倍再加廿万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孰意空言安慰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说过也就忘怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物价高涨是实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加薪尚在开会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"职等吃亏非小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钧座信用有关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所谓名誉要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威信岂可破坏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金价卅万出关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤球卖到两万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"职眷既非巧妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生米难煮熟饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样东西涨价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有薪水跌价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为此呈请照加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折扣不可再打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通货膨胀不休，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于无形税收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剥皮抽筋熬油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钧座何其辣手？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用特哀告泣陈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪鼻涕齐来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"职等变成饿鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂是钧座所快？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏祈准予涨价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恭喜钧座发财，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武的不死文加官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万税！万税！万税！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（文联四四四）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}